replies.body:
There's pros and cons with the hypothetical implementation of my request. If you decide to reside on that side of spectrum that's okay, however, having played more than 6k games + in total on this server, I'm inclined to believe that players wouldn't ultimately use it to bully others. I have been around since season 2, people I've come across with only seldom use their ranks to show superiority. Anyways, I agree that whether this feature would end up being purposeful, or discouraging is quite controversial, but do not be blinded by what the MINORITY of players do.
Cheers, 
A zed Main{{champion:238}}
